==剧情==
本剧讲述带疤化妆师孟茴和抠门总裁沈亿之间的爱情故事<ref>{{cite news|url=https://ent.china.com/gundong/11015422/20191021/37255695.html|title=蒲萄《99分女朋友》杀青 饰演犬系大妞备受期待|date=2019-10-21|publisher=中华网娱乐|accessdate=2020-07-03|archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703201416/https://ent.china.com/gundong/11015422/20191021/37255695.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

